  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      If you wish to use Infinality, use the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>tar xvf ../freetype-infinality-&freetype2-version;-20130514_01-x86_64.tar.bz2 &amp;&amp;
patch -p1 -i freetype-entire-infinality-patchset-20130514-01.patch</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Prepare the package for compilation:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix= \
            --disable-static</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Compile the package:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install the package:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>porg -lD "make -j1 install &amp;&amp;
rm -v /lib/libfreetype.la"</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      If you used the Infinality patchset, as the <systemitem
      class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>sed -i 's/USE_STYLE="DEFAULT"/USE_STYLE="LINUX"/' infinality-settings.sh
porg -lD+ "install -v -m644 infinality-settings.sh /etc/profile.d"</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

